{"article_id":"leDdDy523UsTNnUn","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Monday told reporters","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he is personally taking hydroxychloroquine .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"While Trump 's announcement is worrying from a leadership standpoint ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"it 's not crazy from a health standpoint .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"While the drug has risks ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"if Trump has properly weighed those risks with his doctor","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"it is fair for him to try it .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"A version of this post first appeared in `` Insider Today , '' a daily email","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"written by Henry Blodget and David Plotz .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"To receive it in your inbox ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"please sign up here .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"This is an opinion column .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"The thoughts expressed are those of the author .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"After weeks of going quiet on hydroxychloroquine","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"( HCQ ) ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"the anti-malarial drug","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"he used to tout as a `` game-changer '' for the coronavirus ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"President Trump startled everyone yesterday","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"by announcing","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that he was taking it himself .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"This announcement eclipsed the rest of the day 's news ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"which may be one reason","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Trump brought the topic up again .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"The comments also triggered the same widespread condemnation","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"the President received in the weeks","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"he was talking up the drug in press conferences .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"One aspect of this criticism is fair .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Hydroxychloroquine can have dangerous side effects ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and there 's still no real evidence","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that it works .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"The power of suggestion and leading-by-example , meanwhile , is real .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The announcement by the president of the United States","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"that he considers HCQ 's risks worth taking","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"will likely prompt others to take it , too .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"if taking the drug kills or hurts some people","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"without helping them ,","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"the president will be partially responsible .","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"So Trump should not be talking up HCQ ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"or even sharing his own personal medical choices ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"no matter how much his gut tells him","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"that the drug 's benefits offset its risk .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"But the President 's decision","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"to take the drug himself","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"is reasonable ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"as long as he 's taking it in safe doses","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"with his doctor monitoring him for side effects .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Insider 's hydroxychloroquine expert Andy Dunn asked Dr. David Boulware","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"whether there is any evidence","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that HCQ prevents or reduces the risk of coronavirus infection .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Dr. Boulware is doing a study at the University of Minnesota","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to answer this question right now .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"`` There are no data","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"that pre-exposure prophylaxis is effective","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"to prevent coronavirus .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"It may be .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"It may not be .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"We do not know . ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"In other words , an expert on infectious diseases believes","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that the question","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"of whether HCQ prevents infection","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"is worth a study","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"to answer .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"It might work .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"It might not work .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"We do n't yet know .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"As I noted last month ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"when President Trump was touting HCQ as a game-changer ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"the possibility","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that it might work","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"is persuasive logic in the face of a frightening disease","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"that is otherwise untreatable .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Long before the FDA approved HCQ for emergency use against coronavirus , in fact , many doctors in the US , France , South Korea , and elsewhere were prescribing it","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"based on this logic .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"In the ensuing month , several studies have come out","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"suggesting","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"that HCQ does not work .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"And several other studies have been stopped","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"because the side-effects on some patients were deemed dangerous .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"So the risks are real .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"For some people","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"- Trump apparently included -","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"the remaining possibility","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"that HCQ might work","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"seems enough","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"to offset these risks .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"We all make individual risk assessments and judgments every day .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Some of us view certain activities as `` too risky ''","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and view those","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"who engage in them","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"as reckless and stupid .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Others believe","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that the benefits of the same activities outweigh their risks","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and choose to do them .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Based on what we know about the possible risk/reward trade off","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"of taking hydroxychloroquine ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Trump 's decision is within the realm of reasonable ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"even if you think","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"it 's reckless and stupid .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"It might work .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"It might not work .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"When Dr. Boulware 's study concludes ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"we should know one way or the other .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"A version of this post first appeared in `` Insider Today , '' a daily email","depth":3},{"id":104,"text":"written by Henry Blodget and David Plotz .","depth":3},{"id":105,"text":"To receive it in your inbox ,","depth":3},{"id":106,"text":"please sign up here .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":213,"left":209,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":113,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":108,"right":112,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":112,"left":109,"right":111,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":4,"right":110,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":110,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":208,"left":118,"right":207,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":116,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116